Version 1.8.0
[list]
[*]adds settings to configure the minimum control required in locations before auto-building each building type (defaults to 50% except for temple and minting office which default to 0%)
[*]adds a setting to configure the allowed overbuild levels in a location
[*]fixed bug that makes you lose your settings in the settings window after you switch to a new country (tag)
[*]adds system to allow migrating settings and variables so future updates can be made easier without breaking existing saves
[/list]
